{
  "page": "Wedding of Renly Baratheon and Margaery Tyrell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg/350px-Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"396\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg/525px-Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg/700px-Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell_by_Chillyravenart.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>, by Chillyravenart ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>wedding of Renly Baratheon and Margaery Tyrell</b> occurs in <a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a> near the beginning of the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a> is crowned  <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Andals,_the_Rhoynar,_and_the_First_Men\" title=\"King of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men\">king</a> with the support of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> and marries <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Wedding\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wedding</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Lord of Storm&#39;s End\">Lord of Storm's End</a>, and his lover, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> unsuccessfully plot for Renly's eldest brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>, to put aside Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> and instead wed Loras's sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Robert is mortally wounded by a <a href=\"/index.php/Boar\" title=\"Boar\">boar</a>, Renly approaches Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, and suggests they seize control of the royal children before Cersei can strike.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Eddard refuses the offer, however, and Renly flees <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> along with Loras. Cersei has Eddard <a href=\"/index.php/Arrest_of_Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Arrest of Eddard Stark\">arrested</a> after Robert's death,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Bratheon</a> eventually has Lord Stark executed at the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Renly, Loras, and Loras's kin are among the nobles ordered to swear fealty to Joffrey, Renly's nephew, in King's Landing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Instead of returning to the capital, Renly journeys with Loras to <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a>'s seat in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, and he is proclaimed king by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> and his sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a>, who has fallen in love with her liege lord, rides across the Reach to join Renly after learning he has been crowned.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wedding\">Wedding</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Wedding\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Renly marries Margaery at Highgarden, and Brienne cries bitter tears the night of the celebration.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>, Renly's surviving older brother, does not attend the wedding,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and instead eventually announces his own claim to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg/300px-Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"319\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg/450px-Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg/600px-Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Loras_Tyrell_and_Renly_Baratheon_by_Jroahn.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>, by Jroahn ©</div></div></div>\n<p>During their parley amid Stannis's <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">siege of Storm's End</a>, Renly claims that Margaery was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maid\">maid</a> on their wedding day.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Renly is assassinated by a <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_child\" title=\"Shadow child\">shadow</a> during the siege.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> Loras buries Renly's body in a place near <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As part of an alliance between Houses Tyrell and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a>, the widowed Margaery agrees to marry King Joffrey. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan Tyrell</a> publicly states his sister remains a maiden, as Renly went to war before the marriage was consummated.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup> Margaery claims that Renly had been too drunk on <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> to bed her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Instead of wearing a cloak in the colors of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a> as Renly's widow, Margaery wears a <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_cloak\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s cloak\">maiden's cloak</a> in the colors of House Tyrell when she marries Joffrey. The boy king dies during the <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">royal wedding feast</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup> however, making Margaery twice widowed. Queen Regent Cersei does not believe Mace's claim that Margaery is still a maid<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup> or Margaery's claim that Renly never touched her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_20-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-20\">&#91;20&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Margaery next marries Joffrey's younger brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Taena_Merryweather\" title=\"Taena Merryweather\">Taena Merryweather</a> later tells Cersei, Tommen's mother, about the night of Renly and Margaery's wedding. Taena claims that she helped Renly disrobe for the <a href=\"/index.php/Bedding\" title=\"Bedding\">bedding</a> custom, and that Loras had carried his sister to the bedchamber. Taena casts doubt on Margaery's claim, but admits there was no bloody sheet the next morning to prove the bride had lost her maidenhead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Attendees\">Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Merryweather\" title=\"House Merryweather\"><img alt=\"House Merryweather.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/20px-House_Merryweather.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/30px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/40px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Taena_Merryweather\" title=\"Taena Merryweather\">Taena Merryweather</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\"><img alt=\"House Tarth.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/20px-House_Tarth.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/30px-House_Tarth.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/40px-House_Tarth.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Renly</b>: What am I to do with this brother of mine, <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne</a>? He refuses <a href=\"/index.php/Renly%27s_peach\" title=\"Renly&#39;s peach\">my peach</a>, he refuses <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">my castle</a>, he even shunned my wedding ...<br />\n</p><p><b>Stannis</b>: We both know your wedding was a <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummer</a>'s farce. A year ago you were scheming to make the girl one of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert's</a> whores.<br />\n<b>Renly</b>: A year ago I was scheming to make the girl Robert's queen, but what does it matter? The <a href=\"/index.php/Boar\" title=\"Boar\">boar</a> got Robert and I got <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery</a>. You'll be pleased to know she came to me a <a href=\"/index.php/Maid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maid\">maid</a>.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Stannis</b>: In your bed she's like to die that way.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We should have stayed well out of all <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">this bloody foolishness</a> if you ask me, but once the cow's been milked there's no squirting the cream back up her udder. After <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Lord Puff Fish</a> put that crown on <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly's</a> head, we were into the pudding up to our knees, so here we are to see things through.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_21-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-21\">&#91;21&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Olenna Tyrell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> claimed <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">his daughter</a> was still virgin, but Cersei had her doubts. <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a> had been <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">murdered</a> before he could bed the girl, but she had been wed to <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly</a> first ... A man may prefer the taste of <a href=\"/index.php/Hippocras\" title=\"Hippocras\">hippocras</a>, yet if you set a tankard of <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> before him, he will quaff it quick enough.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Taena</b>: When she wed Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, I helped disrobe him for the bedding. His lordship was a well-made man, and lusty. I saw the proof when we tumbled him into the wedding bed where his bride awaited him as naked as her name day, blushing prettily beneath the coverlets. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras</a> had carried her up the steps himself. <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery</a> may say that the marriage was never consummated, that Lord Renly had drunk too much <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> at the wedding feast, but I promise you, the bit between his legs was anything but weary when last I saw it.<br />\n</p><p><b>Cersei</b>: Did you chance to see the marriage bed the morning after? Did she bleed?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Taena</b>: No sheet was shown, Your Grace.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Taena_Merryweather\" title=\"Taena Merryweather\">Taena Merryweather</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/5457/\">Union Square Signing</a>, July 14, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Arya III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">3.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_31\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 31\">Chapter 31</a>, Catelyn III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47</a>, Eddard XIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 49\">Chapter 49</a>, Eddard XIV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 65\">Chapter 65</a>, Arya V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4